msgid "Rests (plays nothing) for specified number of beats"
msgstr "演奏休息，就是什麼都不播放的意思，這樣一來就可以利用空拍來製作出節奏感"

#: templates/help/studio/tips/blocks/round.html:9
msgid "Reports closest integer to a number"
msgstr "回傳最接近該數值的整數。"

#: templates/help/studio/tips/blocks/round.html:19
#, python-format
msgid ""
"<img src=\"%(url_round)s\" /> gives the rounded value of a number. That "
"means it turns a decimal number into the nearest whole number. For example: "
"<img src=\"%(url_round_5_1)s\" /> is 5, and <img src=\"%(url_round_5_6)s\" "
"/> is 6."
msgstr ""
"<img src=\"%(url_round)s\" /> 會將指定的數字取概數（四捨五入到整數），例如：<img "
"src=\"%(url_round_5_1)s\" /> 會回傳 5，<img src=\"%(url_round_5_6)s\" /> 會回傳 6。"

#: templates/help/studio/tips/blocks/say-for-seconds.html:8
